column16: A SUPER HERO EXTRAVAGANZA THE LIKES OF WHICH THE WORLD HAS NEVER SEEN! Get a front row seat to the hottest ticket in town as we unveil Saturnalia and the Interstellar Circus Spectacular! But there's more to these three rings than meets the EYE! Featuring a wild array of new characters and some of Marvel's all-time most popular super heroes including the Avengers, the Guardians of the Galaxy, and Spider-Man!
column18: | artist:David Baldeon | writer:Karl Kesel | penciller (cover):Todd Nauck
